<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{canonicalUrl}}">
    <meta name="description" content="{{description}}">
    <meta name="author" content="Therr Inc.">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Friends with Habits">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{canonicalUrl}}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{title}}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{description}}">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{title}}">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="{{description}}">
    <link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="dns-prefetch" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend:wght@400;600;800&display=swap">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/assets/images/favicon-habits.ico">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/assets/images/favicon-habits-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/assets/images/favicon-habits-16x16.png">
    <style>
        :root {
            --habits-navy: #102a43;
            --habits-coral: #ff6b35;
            --habits-coral-dark: #e0521e;
            --habits-cream: #fff8f3;
            --habits-text: #243b53;
            --habits-text-muted: #627d98;
            --habits-border: #d9e2ec;
        }
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Lexend', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--habits-text);
            background: var(--habits-cream);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        a { color: var(--habits-coral-dark); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .container {
            max-width: 720px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }
        header.site-header {
            padding: 1.25rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--habits-border);
            background: #fff;
        }
        header.site-header .brand {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--habits-navy);
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }
        .hero {
            padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.15;
            color: var(--habits-navy);
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        .hero p.lede {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
            margin: 0 0 2rem;
            max-width: 540px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .cta {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
            background: var(--habits-coral);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            transition: background 0.15s ease;
        }
        .cta:hover {
            background: var(--habits-coral-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .cta--placeholder {
            background: var(--habits-text-muted);
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        .cta--placeholder:hover { background: var(--habits-text-muted); }
        .cta-note {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
            margin-top: 0.75rem;
        }
        section.steps {
            padding: 3rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--habits-border);
        }
        section.steps h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--habits-navy);
            margin: 0 0 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .step-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .step-list li {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .step-num {
            flex: 0 0 2.25rem;
            width: 2.25rem;
            height: 2.25rem;
            aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--habits-coral);
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .step-body h3 {
            margin: 0.25rem 0 0.25rem;
            font-size: 1.0625rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--habits-navy);
        }
        .step-body p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
        }
        section.why {
            padding: 3rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--habits-border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        section.why h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--habits-navy);
            margin: 0 0 1rem;
        }
        section.why p {
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
            max-width: 520px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
        }
        section.why .stat {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--habits-coral);
            line-height: 1;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }
        footer.site-footer {
            padding: 2rem 0 3rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--habits-border);
            background: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        footer.site-footer .footer-links {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        footer.site-footer .footer-links a {
            margin: 0 0.5rem;
            color: var(--habits-text-muted);
        }
        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .hero { padding: 6rem 0 4rem; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            .hero p.lede { font-size: 1.25rem; }
            .step-list { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
            .step-list li { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; align-items: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="brand">Friends with Habits</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Habits that stick when a friend's on the hook too.</h1>
                <p class="lede">Most habit apps let you give up in private. Friends with Habits doesn't. Pact with a friend, check in daily, and keep each other on streak.</p>
                <a class="cta cta--placeholder" href="#" aria-disabled="true">Coming soon to Google Play</a>
                <div class="cta-note">Internal testing in progress. iOS coming next.</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="steps">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>How it works</h2>
                <ol class="step-list">
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-num">1</span>
                        <div class="step-body">
                            <h3>Create a pact</h3>
                            <p>Pick a habit — workout, reading, meditation, anything daily.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-num">2</span>
                        <div class="step-body">
                            <h3>Invite a friend</h3>
                            <p>You can't do this alone. Your friend joins and becomes your accountability partner.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-num">3</span>
                        <div class="step-body">
                            <h3>Check in daily</h3>
                            <p>Add a photo or quick note as proof. Watch the streak grow together.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="why">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Why accountability changes everything</h2>
                <div class="stat">95%</div>
                <p>People who track habits with a partner stick with them.</p>
                <div class="stat" style="color: var(--habits-text-muted); font-size: 2rem;">10%</div>
                <p>Without a partner, only one in ten do. Solo apps can't bridge that gap. We make accountability the default.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="/terms-of-service">Terms of Service</a>
            </div>
            <div>&copy; Therr Inc. &middot; Part of the Therr family of apps</div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
